---
source: crates/claim/tests/snapshots.rs
expression: "stdout(&repo, &[\"show\", \"payments/libfoo-pin\"], 0)"
---
payments/libfoo-pin  (.claims/payments/libfoo-pin.md)

We pin libfoo at 4.2.

checks:
  [0] cmd (negated)
      run: grep -q 'libfoo==4.2' requirements.txt
      skip: windows CI has no grep
        unless: test -x /usr/bin/grep
        until: 2027-01-01T00:00:00Z
  [1] agent
      instruction: Check the changelog since 5.0 for a CJK fix.

supports:
  - requirements.txt#libfoo
  - other-claim

hub:
  recheck: 30d
  max-age: 120d
